Package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model

package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model
Covers two public interfaces IMatrix and IArithmetical, one own exception DimensionException and five public classes of model package presenting its implementation: Matrix, Calculator, Calculation, ElementDouble, ElementInteger.
